nsecutive-no-op counter (terminate after 3)\n  2. Add sprint-complete detection (all stories in terminal state = exit)\n  3. Kill the current ralph loop manually — it will never produce work\n- **14-4-observability-backend-choice** remains the sole non-done story, permanently blocked by Docker keychain lock. Requires human intervention.\n- **Estimated $7-28 in API credits wasted** on 14 empty sessions."}],"totalDurationMs":93611,"totalTokens":21587,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2482,"cache_read_input_tokens":18854,"output_tokens":250,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2482},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
